00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:52,210
[Chapter 10: Liu Guangcai's Confession]

18
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:56,710
Hello, everyone.

19
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:59,640
My name is Liu Guangcai.

20
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,590
I'm 39 years old.

21
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:06,130
Former head of the Security Department at No. 6 Factory.

22
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:14,430
Li Chao—

23
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,710
I killed him.

24
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,579
After that happened,

25
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:32,960
I was filled with regret

26
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,190
and pain.

27
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,520
I kept reflecting on it.

28
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,400
Later, I realized

29
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,520
the conflict between us

30
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:44,450
probably started

31
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:47,200
when the old factory director was stepping down,

32
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,470
and they needed to promote

33
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:50,280
one of us middle managers

34
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,840
to take over as the new director.

35
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,510
Chief Li.

36
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,820
You're here.

37
00:02:58,050 --> 00:02:59,310
You're looking for me?

38
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:01,390
There's something I want to ask you.

39
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,230
Someone reported me.

40
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,310
Really?

41
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:07,170
They accused me of embezzlement.

42
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:10,150
I had the Security Department look into it,

43
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:13,710
and I got my hands on the report letter.

44
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:15,470
It was your

45
00:03:15,820 --> 00:03:17,220
apprentice who wrote it.

46
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,079
Alright.

47
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:22,270
I'll have a talk with him.

48
00:03:23,590 --> 00:03:24,380
Chief Li,

49
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:26,000
I think the competition

50
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,540
for the factory director should be fair and open.

51
00:03:28,540 --> 00:03:30,120
Shouldn't we avoid

52
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:32,870
playing tricks behind each other's backs?

53
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:39,000
Mr. Liu.

54
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:42,150
I started from the bottom

55
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:44,000
and worked my way here.

56
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,140
It took me 25 years.

57
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:47,750
And you?

58
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:51,310
Your whole family works at this factory.

59
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:54,040
Your parents are technicians,

60
00:03:54,579 --> 00:03:57,050
but they were sent here for re-education.

61
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:02,740
Do you think you're on my level?

62
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:05,790
You're already very lucky to be the head

63
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,000
of the Security Department.

64
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:11,330
You should be grateful and content.

65
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,680
I'd wanted to kill him

66
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,630
for a long, long time.

67
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:22,510
Liu Guangcai,

68
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:23,630
you pissed me off.

69
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:24,350
You know that?

70
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:25,470
I just wanted him dead.

71
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:27,490
You'd better pray I never become the factory director.

72
00:04:27,490 --> 00:04:28,800
Every morning I opened my eyes,

73
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,800
I wanted him dead.

74
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,190
If I really become the factory director…

75
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:32,510
It was like I was possessed.

76
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:35,200
I'll serve your parents,

77
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,560
take care of your wife,

78
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,159
and raise your kid right for you.

79
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,230
Don't worry.

80
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:43,350
If I don't treat your whole family well,

81
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:44,950
then I won't be Li Chao.

82
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:18,790
Actually, I wasn't afraid of him at all.

83
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:23,510
But I knew

84
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,160
I had to act immediately.

85
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:31,800
Because when Li Chao actually got that position,

86
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,400
he'd definitely come for me.

87
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:37,430
But

88
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,040
dealing with someone like Li Chao

89
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,370
took more than impulse.

90
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,950
I needed help.

91
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,360
And right then…

92
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:55,480
two idiots showed up.

93
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:58,159
To me,

94
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,830
your mom is a bus that everyone can ride.

95
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:01,240
And she's the crappiest one out there.

96
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,370
What are you saying?

97
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,070
Li Chao!

98
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:05,800
Come here.

99
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,590
Let go!

100
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,580
Say that again.

101
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:08,920
Say that again!

102
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,760
They managed to get my attention.

103
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,360
And soon,

104
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,830
I discovered a secret.

105
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:31,750
Stop.

106
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,240
Take it out.

107
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,500
Take what out?

108
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,630
You know what I'm talking about.

109
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,890
There's nothing on me.

110
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,800
Nothing.

111
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,110
There's nothing.

112
00:06:40,110 --> 00:06:40,640
I swear…

113
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:42,230
I swear there's nothing.

114
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,560
Yao Binbin,

115
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,030
this isn't the first time

116
00:06:46,030 --> 00:06:47,830
you've stolen from the factory.

117
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,860
What exactly are you trying to do?

118
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:55,430
Yao Binbin was stealing seamless steel pipes.

119
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:58,159
Right then and there,

120
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,870
I had a strong gut feeling—

121
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:03,120
he was making a gun

122
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,730
to kill someone.

123
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,150
Mr. Liu.

124
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:07,960
Mr. Liu.

125
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:09,720
Mr. Liu.

126
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,600
What's the matter?

127
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,790
Yao Binbin, Xu Wenguo,

128
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:12,630
and Director Tang's son

129
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:14,120
got into a fight at the pool hall.

130
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,650
Yao Binbin pulled out a gun.

131
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,250
Yao Binbin pulled out a gun?

132
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,660
Just as I expected.

133
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,680
Anyone hurt?

134
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:22,460
No.

135
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,830
The pool hall owner said the gun didn't go off.

136
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:25,720
With that—

137
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:27,310
I had to help him.

138
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,120
Didn't you promise

139
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,120
you'd only take it out

140
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,850
if that jerk insulted

141
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:31,730
our mom again?

142
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,570
If I hadn't removed the firing pin,

143
00:07:34,570 --> 00:07:36,300
you'd be in deep trouble today.

144
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,460
Sorry, Wenguo.

145
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,360
Go home.

146
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:58,310
I came up with a plan.

147
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:00,720
First,

148
00:08:01,590 --> 00:08:04,050
I needed to find the fake gun Yao Binbin made.

149
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,560
Everyone, stay alert about theft.

150
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,110
Our factory's security is top-notch.

151
00:08:08,110 --> 00:08:09,040
Lock your doors.

152
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,240
Every family sleeps with doors unlocked.

153
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,270
No one picks up lost items on the road.

154
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,190
If you go out, lock your door.

155
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:15,250
Everyone leaves a spare key outside—

156
