158
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,120
What I needed to do next

159
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,910
was give it a firing pin.

160
00:09:58,550 --> 00:09:59,390
Next,

161
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:01,680
I had to create

162
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,030
an opportunity

163
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:05,630
for Yao Binbin to fire this gun.

164
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,040
Chief Li?

165
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,440
Chief Li?

166
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,480
It's me.

167
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:15,840
Chief Li,

168
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:17,080
are you going fishing?

169
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,790
Yes.

170
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,740
Come, have some tea.

171
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:19,960
No, thanks.

172
00:10:20,430 --> 00:10:21,150
I came here

173
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:23,440
to talk to you about something.

174
00:10:24,970 --> 00:10:26,330
Yao, why don't you…

175
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:28,150
Master, I'll wait for you outside.

176
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:28,840
Alright.

177
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,400
Okay.

178
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:32,180
Sit, sit.

179
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,860
Congratulations in advance.

180
00:10:38,590 --> 00:10:41,120
I heard that the position of factory director

181
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,320
is surely yours.

182
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,380
After we talked last time,

183
00:10:45,530 --> 00:10:47,060
everything clicked for me.

184
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,200
Really?

185
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,980
Yes.

186
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,390
Moreover,

187
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,800
I'll need to work hard

188
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,380
under your leadership in the future.

189
00:10:55,730 --> 00:10:56,760
That's more like it.

190
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,770
The more you want to take someone down,

191
00:10:58,770 --> 00:11:00,910
the more you need to make them trust you.

192
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,510
Best if you can even pass as a friend.

193
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:03,650
You're so young,

194
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:06,150
exactly what our factory needs.

195
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:07,970
Work hard.

196
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,740
Your future is bright.

197
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:10,840
I...

198
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,360
Thank you, Director.

199
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,150
Thank you, Director.

200
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:14,840
Bit too early for that.

201
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,770
It's not proper.

202
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,030
The appointment hasn't been finalized yet.

203
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:18,910
You're

204
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:20,550
heading out to fish soon?

205
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:21,840
Leaving in a bit.

206
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:23,750
Going alone?

207
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:24,630
Yeah.

208
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:26,910
Let me go with you.

209
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,920
No need.

210
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:30,000
Fishing isn't hunting wolves.

211
00:11:30,100 --> 00:11:31,900
Going alone keeps the mind calm.

212
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,750
He was going alone.

213
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,550
That was perfect.

214
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,930
To get Yao Binbin to make a move,

215
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:52,450
I had to work on Cui Lizhen.

216
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,550
You and Chief Li

217
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:56,480
have a special connection, right?

218
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,060
This time,

219
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,770
I don't know why,

220
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:02,890
but Chief Li insists on adding you

221
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:04,270
and Xu Wenguo

222
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,990
to the layoff list.

223
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,260
I can't understand it either.

224
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:10,370
Maybe you should

225
00:12:10,610 --> 00:12:12,270
have a word with him in private.

226
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:12,790
No.

227
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:14,080
If there's any conflict,

228
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,600
you two can try to talk it out.

229
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,490
Your two sons

230
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,320
often have conflicts with Chief Li.

231
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,320
If something really happens,

232
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,270
how is the Security Department

233
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,480
supposed to handle it?

234
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,600
Where is that jerk now?

235
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,120
I'll go find him right away

236
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,600
-to make it clear to him!
-Calm down, Ms. Cui.

237
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,550
I've been working here for decades…

238
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:27,720
I mean well.

239
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,790
I mean well. You…

240
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:29,510
Ms. Cui.

241
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:31,300
Ms. Cui?

242
00:12:31,790 --> 00:12:32,420
Ms. Cui?

243
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:34,240
Ms. Cui!

244
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:35,990
Cui Lizhen was so cooperative.

245
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:38,760
Binbin, Binbin!

246
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,000
Mr. Liu,

247
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,800
what's wrong?

248
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:42,640
You need to

249
00:12:42,780 --> 00:12:44,040
go to the hospital now.

250
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,720
Your mom collapsed.

251
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,630
What happened to my mom?

252
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:47,420
Li Chao,

253
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,320
Chief Li,

254
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:51,550
put your mother and brother

255
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,790
on the layoff list.

256
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,050
Where's Li Chao?

257
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,330
He's fishing at the reservoir.

258
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,600
Li Chao!

259
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,550
Why did you put my mom

260
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:07,770
and brother on the layoff list?

261
00:13:07,770 --> 00:13:08,880
Your brother's business

262
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,020
is none of your concern.

263
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:12,270
As for your mom, tell her to come see me herself

264
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,680
after she scrubs up real nice.

265
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:15,740
I'll blow your brains out right here!

266
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:25,000
I overestimated the power of that gun.

267
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:27,000
Li Chao

268
00:13:28,180 --> 00:13:29,940
wasn't killed on the spot.

269
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,630
Brat.

270
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:40,630
How...

271
00:13:42,670 --> 00:13:45,040
How dare you shoot me?

272
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,910
Stop there!

273
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,480
Actually, Binbin

274
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:02,790
had already done everything for me.

275
00:14:04,530 --> 00:14:06,460
I shouldn't have stepped in again.

276
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,450
I should have just stayed there

277
00:14:12,930 --> 00:14:14,930
and waited for Li Chao to die slowly.

278
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,000
But that night,

279
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,520
I was too impulsive.

280
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,870
It was like I was possessed.

281
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,200
Chief Li.

282
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,300
Chief Li, are you alright?

283
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,670
Chief Li?

284
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,680
What happened to you?

285
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:43,800
Come on.

286
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:46,870
Are you okay?

287
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:50,000
What happened to you?

288
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:52,480
You'll be fine.

289
00:14:53,170 --> 00:14:54,030
You'll be fine.

290
00:14:54,550 --> 00:14:55,410
You'll be fine.

291
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,060
You'll be fine.

292
00:15:46,670 --> 00:15:48,100
At that moment…

293
00:15:50,510 --> 00:15:52,000
I couldn't tell if I was hallucinating

294
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,060
or if there really was someone there.

295
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:57,670
My mind was a mess.

296
00:16:00,010 --> 00:16:01,290
According to the plan,

297
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:03,840
I should've gone straight to the repair shop

298
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,770
and caught Yao Binbin with the gun.

299
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:08,250
But for some inexplicable reason…

300
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:13,620
I went back to the staff dormitory first.

301
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:44,390
It was her.

302
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:47,270
The one who ran off from the reservoir

303
00:16:47,270 --> 00:16:48,330
must have been her.

304
00:16:49,730 --> 00:16:51,030
That was my first instinct

305
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:53,430
when I saw Chen Su'e at the staff dormitory.

306
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,400
She saw me.

307
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,950
I really didn't see clearly.

308
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:05,900
I...

309
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,400
I chased after him.

310
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,890
Yao Binbin ran very fast.

311
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,240
I wasn't as fast as him

312
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,970
and failed to catch up with him.

313
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,859
When I reached the reservoir,

314
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:17,160
I heard a loud bang…

315
00:17:19,319 --> 00:17:21,130
and then the guy fell down.

316
00:17:27,349 --> 00:17:29,140
So you saw Yao Binbin

317
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:31,300
shoot and kill Li Chao,

318
00:17:31,830 --> 00:17:32,550
right?

319
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:38,200
I knew she was terrified,

320
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,220
but at that moment,

321
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:43,200
I was even more nervous than her.

322
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:50,200
Whether to kill Chen Su'e or not—

323
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,050
I wanted her to make that decision herself.

324
00:17:53,050 --> 00:17:53,900
Aunt Chen,

325
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:55,840
you've told us this

326
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:57,970
because you put justice above family.

327
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:59,350
We'll protect you.

328
00:18:01,550 --> 00:18:02,650
I heard

329
00:18:03,030 --> 00:18:04,920
the surgery you had a few years ago

330
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,660
cost over 30,000 yuan and still

331
00:18:06,660 --> 00:18:08,060
hasn't been reimbursed.

332
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,660
I've reported this situation

333
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:12,070
to the factory.

334
00:18:13,890 --> 00:18:16,210
We'll cover 10,000 yuan for you first,

335
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,200
alright?

336
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:22,960
To be honest,

337
00:18:25,140 --> 00:18:26,200
I kept hesitating

338
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:28,190
whether to kill Chen Su'e or not.

339
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:31,100
She's weak

340
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:33,440
and easy to control.

341
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,190
For a while,

342
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,760
I completely gave up

343
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:40,250
on the idea of killing her.

344
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:44,460
But that prison guard,

345
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:45,960
Du Xiangdong,

346
00:18:47,030 --> 00:18:49,270
came to the factory again and again.

347
00:18:56,700 --> 00:18:57,720
Step back!

348
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:58,550
What are you doing?

349
00:18:58,550 --> 00:18:59,810
And the real firing pin

350
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:01,660
was eventually found.

351
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,880
That was when everything

352
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:07,340
started slipping out of my control.

353
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:13,990
More surprisingly…

354
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:46,280
[Attached: photo of Xu Wenguo]

355
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:50,210
Xu Wenguo broke out of prison.

356
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:58,000
He was definitely

357
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:01,230
going to look for Chen Su'e.

358
00:20:11,070 --> 00:20:12,550
I had to get to her first.

359
00:20:18,270 --> 00:20:19,110
Mr. Liu,

360
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,670
what brings you here?

361
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:23,720
I heard you're not feeling well.

362
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:25,690
We at the factory have been worried.

363
00:20:25,690 --> 00:20:27,510
The director asked me to check on you.

364
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:29,110
These are some gifts for you.

365
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,680
No need, no need.

366
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,760
I'm in good health.

367
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,190
Thanks for your concern.

368
00:20:35,990 --> 00:20:36,840
Last time,

369
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:38,590
you got 10,000 yuan

370
00:20:38,970 --> 00:20:40,900
for your medical expenses, right?

371
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:42,650
I talked to my superiors again,

372
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:44,120
and the director sent me

373
00:20:44,780 --> 00:20:45,920
to bring you the remaining

374
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,060
20,000 yuan.

375
00:20:47,300 --> 00:20:49,160
It's not convenient to talk here.

376
00:20:56,830 --> 00:20:57,890
Let's talk inside.

377
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,110
I'm just here

378
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:08,790
on behalf of the factory to deliver the money.

379
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:11,090
Please write me a receipt.

380
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:12,510
I've got to hurry back.

381
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:20,240
Okay.

382
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:32,590
The receipt is for the factory?

383
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:34,530
Yes.

384
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:40,410
Also,

385
00:21:40,810 --> 00:21:43,070
the director told me to pass on a message.

386
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:45,000
He said you don't need

387
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:48,480
to worry about anything.

388
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:51,720
Just focus on getting better

389
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:54,530
and come back to work as soon as you can.

390
00:21:59,490 --> 00:22:00,810
In two more years,

391
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:04,560
you'll be able to retire and receive a pension.

392
00:22:05,470 --> 00:22:07,330
Please thank the director for me.

393
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:09,030
No need for that.

394
00:22:09,390 --> 00:22:11,200
We're all family at No. 6 Factory.

395
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,040
This is just

396
00:22:12,070 --> 00:22:13,070
what we should do!

397
00:22:52,110 --> 00:22:53,830
After Chen Su'e was taken care of,

398
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:55,240
next up was Xu Wenguo.

399
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:57,510
I knew that guy very well.

400
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,270
He was a bookworm

401
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,880
and a thinker.

402
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,160
Not easy to deal with.

403
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:04,960
My men told me

404
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:07,790
Cui Lizhen received a remittance slip.

405
00:23:08,700 --> 00:23:11,560
Du Xiangdong seemed to have picked up on something.

406
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,930
In this world,

407
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:15,900
the one who wanted to find Xu Wenguo more than I did

408
00:23:15,900 --> 00:23:16,900
was Du Xiangdong.

409
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,940
As long as he was alive,

410
00:23:20,270 --> 00:23:22,930
he'd keep trying to overturn Yao Binbin's case.

411
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:27,240
I had to get rid of him.

412
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:33,800
I once asked Zheng Sanchuang

413
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:35,750
to take care of Xu Wenguo in prison.

414
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:37,480
I realized

415
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,010
he was about to be released.

416
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,000
I've confessed everything.

417
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:58,780
Killing Li Chao

418
00:23:59,230 --> 00:23:59,960
and Chen Su'e

419
00:24:00,590 --> 00:24:02,420
and pinning it on Xu Wenguo and Yao Binbin—

420
00:24:02,420 --> 00:24:03,380
it was all me.

421
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,720
I'm sorry, guys.

422
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,900
I dragged you down with me.

423
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:12,810
They were just errand boys.

424
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,660
I accept any legal judgment

425
00:24:15,690 --> 00:24:16,690
against me.

426
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,510
My only request

427
00:24:20,990 --> 00:24:23,120
is that the leaders of No. 6 Factory

428
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,890
treat my family well.

429
00:24:42,950 --> 00:24:46,260
I've worked at No. 6 Factory my whole life.

430
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:51,030
You've all seen my performance.

431
00:24:54,310 --> 00:24:55,480
If I had the chance

432
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:57,070
to live again,

433
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,280
I'd definitely leave

434
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,620
and see the outside world.

435
00:25:14,610 --> 00:25:17,290
[No. 6 Machine Factory]

436
00:25:37,630 --> 00:25:38,790
I plead guilty.

437
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:40,600
That's it.

438
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:57,440
Come on,

439
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,520
let's talk about

440
00:25:59,550 --> 00:26:00,610
Yao Binbin's case.

441
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:12,270
Is there anything we can do

442
00:26:12,270 --> 00:26:13,200
for his family?

443
00:26:14,510 --> 00:26:15,960
The country has passed

444
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:17,270
a compensation law this year.

445
00:26:17,270 --> 00:26:19,310
The organization will handle it.

446
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:20,640
Mr. Su,

447
00:26:21,090 --> 00:26:22,330
in Yao Binbin's case,

448
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,930
we hold no responsibility.

449
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:26,360
First, there was no forced confession.

450
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:27,720
He confessed on his own.

451
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:29,460
The evidence chain was complete too.

452
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,630
And besides,

453
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,310
he really did make a gun, fire it,

454
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:33,310
injure Li Chao,

455
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:34,910
flee, and snatch the gun.

456
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:35,920
Those are all facts.

457
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,890
He had multiple offenses against him.

458
00:26:37,890 --> 00:26:39,820
But he didn't know it was a real gun,

459
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:43,350
nor did he know there were real bullets inside.

460
00:26:43,350 --> 00:26:44,940
He had no intent to kill.

461
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:51,550
No matter what,

462
00:26:52,130 --> 00:26:53,170
I made the arrest

463
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:55,130
and conducted the interrogation.

464
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:57,840
I'll take whatever punishment

465
00:26:58,040 --> 00:26:59,500
the higher-ups decide on.

466
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:05,490
Why do you sound so guilty?

467
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:08,820
Say that again.

468
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,530
I made the arrest

469
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:13,240
and conducted the interrogation.

470
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,730
Whatever my punishment is,

471
00:27:16,030 --> 00:27:16,830
be it a serious demerit

472
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:17,660
or dismissal,

473
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:18,860
I'll accept it.

474
00:27:20,020 --> 00:27:21,750
You should've said so earlier.

475
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,410
Come on, stop working for a bit.

476
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:27,580
Come out. I have a few words to say.

477
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,680
Here's the deal.

478
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:41,880
Regarding Yao Binbin's case,

479
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,640
do you bear some responsibility?

480
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,190
Yes.

481
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:48,400
But the main responsibility lies with me.

482
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:50,200
I take the main responsibility.

483
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:53,340
We can't afford to make mistakes.

484
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:55,140
Even the smallest one

485
00:27:55,750 --> 00:27:58,160
could cost lives.

486
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:06,920
I've already submitted a transfer request to the bureau,

487
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:08,250
and it's been approved.

488
00:28:10,510 --> 00:28:11,240
Next Monday,

489
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:13,570
I'll report to the Nanjie Police Station.

490
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,640
If any of you

491
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,510
need my help in the future,

492
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:23,300
just say the word.

493
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:10,000
Why are you standing in my way?

494
00:29:13,350 --> 00:29:14,160
Tonight,

495
00:29:15,530 --> 00:29:17,330
we'd like to treat you to dinner.

496
00:29:21,370 --> 00:29:22,430
A farewell dinner?

497
00:29:25,110 --> 00:29:26,640
We're not parting ways yet.

498
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:31,400
I finally get to leave work early for once.

499
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:34,200
I'm going home to have dinner with my wife and kids.

500
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:16,580
[Serve the People]

501
00:30:22,070 --> 00:30:22,710
Here, yours is ready.

502
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:23,720
[Fenfang Trotters]

503
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:23,920
I told you so many times already.

504
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:25,590
Take care, come again.

505
00:30:28,070 --> 00:30:29,200
Pack up and leave.

506
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:29,960
Pack up and leave!

507
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,920
Stop selling! Pack up and go!

508
00:30:31,970 --> 00:30:32,950
Pack up! Hurry up.

509
00:30:32,950 --> 00:30:34,510
How many times have I told you?

510
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:35,550
Pack up and leave.

511
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,750
Hurry up. Leave!

512
00:30:36,750 --> 00:30:37,830
I told you so many times already.

513
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:39,070
Why wouldn't you listen?

514
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:41,310
Wait, wait. I have customers here.

515
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:42,750
Don't touch my things.

516
00:30:42,750 --> 00:30:43,940
Don't touch my things.

517
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:45,200
Are you saying you've done nothing wrong?

518
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:46,510
That's not what I mean, sir.

519
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:47,790
I have customers here.

520
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:48,860
My shop is being renovated.

521
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:49,720
Once it's done, I won't come back here.

522
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:50,160
Move aside!

523
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:50,920
Please put them down.

524
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,790
I know what you mean.

525
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:52,720
What's going on?

526
00:30:53,110 --> 00:30:54,440
-Xiangyang.
-Where are you taking those things?

527
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:56,620
Aren't you Captain Zhang from the Criminal Police Team?

528
00:30:56,620 --> 00:30:57,550
Nice to meet you.

529
00:30:58,390 --> 00:30:59,160
What's going on?

530
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,220
It started raining, so I set up a tarp.

531
00:31:01,570 --> 00:31:02,990
But she's occupying public space.

532
00:31:02,990 --> 00:31:04,440
It's against the rules.

533
00:31:05,010 --> 00:31:06,640
We've warned her so many times.

534
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:08,220
It's not easy for ordinary folks to make a living.

535
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:09,250
Give her a break.

536
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:10,610
Understood, understood.

537
00:31:10,610 --> 00:31:11,640
So how about

538
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,470
we eat something together?

539
00:31:12,470 --> 00:31:13,200
Come on, sit down.

540
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,530
No need, Captain Zhang.

541
00:31:14,830 --> 00:31:15,550
You don't want anything?

542
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:17,070
If you haven't taken it down by tomorrow,

543
00:31:17,070 --> 00:31:18,640
we'll confiscate everything.

544
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,200
Alright.

545
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,350
This is the last warning.

546
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:21,480
Okay.

547
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,220
Xiangyang, sit down.

548
00:31:23,220 --> 00:31:23,690
Sit.

549
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:28,550
Xiangyang, what do you want to eat?

550
00:31:28,550 --> 00:31:29,480
Bring me a glass

551
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,230
and a trotter soup.

552
00:31:30,230 --> 00:31:31,190
Alright.

553
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:50,520
Here you go.

554
00:31:50,520 --> 00:31:51,200
Take your time.

555
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:53,060
Call me if you need anything else.

556
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:01,070
Mi's martyr title got approved.

557
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:03,070
His wife asked me to thank you

558
00:32:03,070 --> 00:32:04,330
for testifying for him

559
00:32:04,380 --> 00:32:06,640
and proving that he was indeed innocent.

560
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:13,640
Mi was a great criminal police officer.

561
00:32:18,670 --> 00:32:19,870
I'm not as good as him.

562
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:23,950
Maybe I'm just not cut out to be a criminal police officer.

563
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,640
Why are you so humble today?

564
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:30,640
It's a pity that Mi died.

565
00:32:36,810 --> 00:32:39,350
But at least he didn't die for nothing.

566
00:32:40,670 --> 00:32:42,730
Liu Guangcai confessed everything.

567
00:32:42,780 --> 00:32:45,040
The No. 6 Factory case is finally solved.

568
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:48,210
Xiangdong.

569
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:50,740
This one's for you.

570
00:32:53,070 --> 00:32:54,470
Your instinct was right.

571
00:32:57,890 --> 00:32:59,900
Yao Binbin didn't kill anyone.

572
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:08,720
And?

573
00:33:12,110 --> 00:33:13,910
His family will be compensated.

574
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:16,070
We're talking to his mom.

575
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:16,960
That's it?

576
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:22,750
That was a life.

577
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:29,440
Mr. Su took all the blame.

578
00:33:33,120 --> 00:33:35,470
He asked for a place for you in the Criminal Police Team

579
00:33:35,470 --> 00:33:36,660
before he left.

580
00:33:55,890 --> 00:33:57,170
Sign this.

581
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,880
How about Yao Binbin?

